msgstr "$$ (\\\\tau+1,\\\\tau+1+j+1)-(\\\\tau,\\\\tau+j)=(1,2). $$"

#: src/12-end-to-end.md:263
msgid ""
"同理，$i$ 读支给 $(1,0)\\\\mapsto(1,1)$，`i+1` 读支给 $(1,-1)\\"
