#: src/appendices.md:1425
msgid ""
"记 $\\\\operatorname{Rel}(X,Y)=2^{X\\\\times Y}$，并设 $R,S\\\\in\\"
"\\operatorname{Rel}(X,Y)$、$Q\\\\in\\\\operatorname{Rel}(Y,Z)$。补集总是相对"
"于显式 universe。复合固定为先走 $R$、再走 $Q$。"
msgstr ""
"Enregistreu $\\\\operatorname{Rel}(X,Y)=2^{X\\\\times Y}$ i configureu $R,S\\"
"\\in\\\\operatorname{Rel}(X,Y)$, $Q\\\\in\\\\operatorname{Rel}(Y,Z)$. El "
"complement sempre és relatiu a l'univers explícit. El compost es fixa primer "
"com a $R$ i després $Q$."

#: src/appendices.md:1427
